00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:17.879
Because

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.480
I want to live.

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:22.079
You want to live?

00:08:22.759 --> 00:08:23.560
Alright.

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.279
As long as you say

00:08:25.279 --> 00:08:26.839
K left the room last night,

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:28.360
I'll let you go immediately.

00:08:29.839 --> 00:08:31.879
But if you don't say it,

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:33.639
I will show

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.399
