00:08:36.480 --> 00:08:38.639
You have three seconds.

00:08:38.639 --> 00:08:39.240
One.

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:40.399
Two.

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:43.240
He...

00:08:56.826 --> 00:09:00.809
